ggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒即係句歌詞可以寫做<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 長過ぎた夜に &rdquo; ？？<br />\n<br />\n初學日文 撈亂 &ldquo;すぎ &rdquo; 同&ldquo; すぎる/過ぎる &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n乜乜すぎ (很乜乜的)<br />\n<br />\nすぎる=過ぎる (過去了) = 過ぎた (過去式)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cf0c30a536b229c57ab7283f66219b5c2d6f01","tid":131495,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面嘅巴打們 好多謝你地詳盡解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒即係句歌詞可以寫做<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 長過ぎた夜に &rdquo; ？？<br />\n<br />\n初學日文 撈亂 &ldquo;すぎ &rdquo; 同&ldquo; すぎる/過ぎる &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n乜乜すぎ (很乜乜的)<br />\n<br />\nすぎる=過ぎる (過去了) = 過ぎた (過去式)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一直都係すぎる/過ぎる 係同一個字黎.........<br />\n係解超過普通的程度   姐係中文既&quot;太....&quot;  <br />\n同&quot;很&quot;又有少少分別  程度再高啲<br />\n當然都可以有其他意思 但就呢句歌詞係咁既意思"},{"pid":"e4634cf2839b727bcc3a83254b882238048b82d4","tid":131495,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面嘅巴打們 好多謝你地詳盡解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒即係句歌詞可以寫做<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 長過ぎた夜に &rdquo; ？？<br />\n<br />\n初學日文 撈亂 &ldquo;すぎ &rdquo; 同&ldquo; すぎる/過ぎる &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n乜乜すぎ (很乜乜的)<br />\n<br />\nすぎる=過ぎる (過去了) = 過ぎた (過去式)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一直都係すぎる/過ぎる 係同一個字黎.........<br />\n係解超過普通的程度   姐係中文既&quot;太....&quot;  <br />\n同&quot;很&quot;又有少少分別  程度再高啲<br />\n當然都可以有其他意思 但就呢句歌詞係咁既意思</blockquote><br />\n好感激巴打用心答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 日語初學JJ 覺得好多文法會好confuse<br />\n<br />\n例如 好多關於 日語漢字/詞 唔識讀 <br />\n多個い音多個う音又唔同意思...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539df08d90b8a1185d3eacec8034047a9df2f567","tid":131495,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面嘅巴打們 好多謝你地詳盡解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講晒即係句歌詞可以寫做<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo; 長過ぎた夜に &rdquo; ？？<br />\n<br />\n初學日文 撈亂 &ldquo;すぎ &rdquo; 同&ldquo; すぎる/過ぎる &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n乜乜すぎ (很乜乜的)<br />\n<br />\nすぎる=過ぎる (過去了) = 過ぎた (過去式)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以，但寫すぎる／すぎた會比較自然<br />\n<br />\n另外，すぎ すぎる基本上係同一個意思 (同解 太過...)<br />\n<br />\n之前又打錯字，等我再試下解釋得清楚少少<br />\n<br />\nすぎる 係動詞， 過去式係すぎた<br />\nすぎ 係將形容詞名詞化 過去式係すぎだった<br />\n<br />\n好眼瞓，瞓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ecfda24dfdf85c292d5c69e07e84d8fb85dd38a","tid":131495,"uid":35004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T07:51:12.000Z","msg":"すぎる 同 過ぎる其實可以係一樣意思<br />\n有好多漢字因爲複雜同可能冇乜人識讀<br />\n考慮到漢字嘅普及程度，唔同嘅語境會有唔同寫法<br />\n例如小朋友嘅書會比較多假名，因為佢地識嘅漢字不多<br />\n不過當然，有好多日文字係同音嘅，所以有好多假名嘅時候都會睇埋上文下理"}]}